  "texts": [
    "In this paper, we propose a theory-grounded iterative-prompting-based planning approach to generating suspenseful stories.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first attempt at suspenseful story generation with LLMs.",
    "Through extensive human evaluations, we prove that our method is more capable of producing suspenseful stories than the baseline method.",
    "Our in-depth analysis of factors that affect suspense perception is also informative for story generation researchers and practitioners.",
    "Our system is developed for suspenseful story generation in English and our method has not been tested in other languages."
